desc: Celebrating your pet's special moments with nutritious and delicious cakes, snacks and treats for dogs & cats. Made with love and by our main chef - certified from North American Veterinary Community. All ingredients are human-grade, no hidden sugar, no salt, no additives or artificial coloring and no preservatives.
